commit.message:
Add 18 new filetype icons

Adds Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and bar chart icons. Also adds two journal bookmark icons.
Add two new eomjis, plus fill variations for all
Fixes #437: make file-earmark variations consistent

Fix some broken icons

- Fixes #423: Update arrow-up-square-fil
- Fixes #415: Properly name grip-horizontal and grip-vertical
Fix up paths from symbol-ification in Figma
Fixes #375: correct names of calculator icons
Clean up paths on alarms and stopwatchs, fixes #361
Add two new icons: plug-fill and scissors
Redraw several icons with cleaner paths

Redraw some tools and real world icons

- Redraw brush entirely, make it all outlined
- New brush-fill variant
- Redrew bucket and bucket-fill
- Redrew speaker to be outlined, added speaker-fill variant
Redraw two comms icons to fix overlapping paths

Updated geo icons

- Smooth out map again
- Added map-fill variant
- Redesigned geo-alt to be outline version, then created geo-alt-fill
- Added compass-fill

Redraw and extend bookmark icons

- Widens and rounds the original bookmark icons
- Moved icons from corner cutouts to center of each icon so we can do fill variants
- Added x, star, and heart variants
- Added fill versions of all existing and new bookmark icons

Add new icons

- cup-fill
- geo-fill
- pen-fill
- pencil-fill
- trophy-fill
- vector-pen
Redraw and enlarge pen and pencil icons
Update arrows on download and upload icons to match arrow icons
Updated geo icons to make map and pin simpler and taller
Simplify bar chart and graph icons
Update video camera icons to simplify paths and make them more pixel perfect

Redraw some communication icons to simplify paths

- Flag icons now larger
- Inboxes icons slightly tweaked, and no overlapping paths
- Share icons have simpler paths

Redraw several real world icons

- Simplify paths on books, bicycle, newspaper, doors, and closed
- Redrew cup icon to be larger
- Redrew trophy icon to simplify it a lot
Redraw several UI and graphics icons for simpler paths

Clean up commerce icons

- Updated wallets to have cleaner paths
- Updated baskets to have consistent paths, no overlaps, better pixels
- Redraw trucks for cleaner paths
Redraw arrows and box arrows
Redraw alerts, warnings, and signs
Redraw archive icons for pixel perfect handles
Fixes #355: Fix paths on striped cone icons
Add three more file icons to round out file sets, new image variants

Update and unify all file icons

- File icons are now taller by 2px, making them appear more like documents
- All icons updated to use unified shapes
- 40 new icons (mostly earmark options, but also new file types)

Update calendar icons

- Redrawn for consistency
- Add 4 new icons, two options for calendar-x icons
